      "rationale": "Experimental boundary conditions are documented in the test report TR-2024-VAD-001. Fluid viscosity was measured at test temperature with ±3% uncertainty; inlet flow rate controlled to ±1.5%. Pump geometry was measured by CMM with ±0.05 mm tolerance. Simulation boundary conditions were set to experimental nominal values. Temperature-dependent viscosity variation was not propagated into the CFD model. Achieved level 3."
