      "rationale": "Quantitative comparison metrics are reported (nRMSE = 18.3%, Bland–Altman bias and LoA). Prediction intervals from Monte Carlo UQ are included. Experimental measurement uncertainty is reported as ±12% (CV) based on inter-run repeatability. The comparison covers 4 of 5 operating points within the 95% PI; one outlier at 2.5 L/min/2400 RPM falls outside the PI. Achieved level 3 reflects adequate quantitative comparison with one unresolved outlier."
